Class EdgeFilterProducts

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.imageProcessing.EdgeFilterProducts

  • public class EdgeFilterProducts
extends java.lang.Object
    a wrapper to hold the results of an edge image filter, specifically the gradient X, gradient Y, the combined gradients XY, and the theta image.
